reviews.text: 質素比剛開業時差了很多，賣相還可以但質素跟快餐店差不多。
5-13 同老公去咗北角健威商場，試咗日式海鮮石燒定食，食材新鮮配以溫石無油燒烤，健康新口味值得一試! 啱哂我呢個怕食生冷易有菌刺身嘅食家! 驚喜只需加$40元又嚐到半份鑽歧烏冬，又送埋日式湯、沙律㖭!😋👍🎉🎉
繁忙時段須倫後入座，餐廳尚整潔。女員工欠奉笑容。

Just not good. First time encountering curry that taste like spicy soy sauce. And meals didn’t come at the same time. One came after the other one, way after. 

If I want rice with soy sauce, I’d go to Tai Hing next door with Chinese barbecue pork.
叫咗個海鮮火鍋，但係帶子唔新鮮，蝦同埋生毫已經先行整熟咗，我懷疑係呢間餐廳見D海鮮就嚟過期，先整熟，咁就唔會蝕咗D材料，好可能係咁！

reviews.text: Free 3 hours parking required of $500 consumed by Alipay! It is no longer a good place for parking!
Very good for electronic marchine.
a very convenience shopping mall with all needs for daily life, various kind of restaurant s, supermarket and grocery shops.
You can find some good shops and a few reasonable restaurants in Fitfort.

For car parking, it provides good condition of car parking environment.  They provide day parking until midnight and also provided max. 3 hrs free parking for only HK$200 spending in plaza.  Hence it seems to be the lowest price day parking available in North Point. (Last updated on 31/12/2017)
